<item>
            <title>[OPENJPA-881] Enable connection pooling for testcases. </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-881</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Test configurations currently use dbcp with MaxIdle=0, effectively no connection pool. For Derby this doesn&apos;t have much of an effect but with other databases, like DB2, setting MaxIdle=2 can dramatically improve the time taken to run the tests. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12413556">OPENJPA-881</key>
            <summary>Enable connection pooling for testcases. </summary>
